{
  "stem": "22869.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were afraid of pressure, of world pressure, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so we're now in the end of 1944, and we're beginning-- we already hear the-- like I said, the artillery from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That might have been yet a few days away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there is an announcement coming into the camps that they're going to evacuate Birkenau, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they come out, and they give us certain kind of a rules or regulations about when it's going to be, and how it's going to be, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had a council of-- if I may call it, the council of sages, of old timers, of the guys who were already in Auschwitz three years, who know it all, who are-- who know the psychology of the Germans, how they would act, react to any kind of an incident.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have a meeting one day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it didn't have to be secret, because once you were in the camp, the Germans were outside.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we weren't worried about this meeting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were chosen, maybe 20, 25 guys, all of them who were already longer, or about two and a half, three years in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None of them who were in this council-- if I call it that for a purpose-- were any newcomer Hungarians, because we thought, what do they know about the Germans?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know better.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we have this meeting, we decide, because we already knew that the Germans are going to give us bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to give us drinks, and they're going to give us salami.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're going to tell us, you'll get food galore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're going to go on this big march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they had no vehicles, they were in such trouble to transport us.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
